    "actual_capabilities": [
      "Lists and searches available inference.sh apps by category, name, and featured status.",
      "Runs hosted image, video, audio, text, search, 3D, and utility apps through `belt app run`.",
      "Generates sample input files and retrieves app schemas before execution.",
      "Tracks long-running tasks and saves task results to files when requested.",
      "Supports local media inputs for apps that accept uploaded files.",
      "Documents authentication through browser login or the INFSH_API_KEY environment variable."
